review_title: the 2 level is way to hard and dumb
one_reviews_text: the 2 level is way to hard and dumb

I was looking for just such a game: a bit of funny & no scary archery. I was always thinking of getting "Die Wolf" when it is on sale but this funny archery game is just perfect as well! Thank you Devs! This is just one of these games you keep on your drive and come back to it once in a while for a bit of fun!
Not aggressive just fun, it requires a sure shot to hit the little rascals. Thank You. God Bless
Lots of fun.  Just the right amount of challenge.  The low res option brightens up the scene considerably for more fun.
